snippet.title: Absolute Force Online Trailer
snippet.description:
Absolute Force Online Trailer. Get the guns ! Join us on Facebook & Twitter http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial & http://twitter.com/gamenewstrailer. Cinematic trailer for AFO : Absolute Force Online, a FPS in which players can take on the roles of hardened mercenaries !

Absolute Force Online Trailer. Close beta coming November, 2012. Subscribe now to get the latest game teasers, gameplay trailers, videogame walkthrough and ingame videos !
